{
  "texts": [
    "4) We combine the data in step 1 and refined data for retraining ELE-SAM to improve accuracy in subsequent iterations.",
    "The loop of SAM-assisted labeling, manual refinement, and retraining is repeated until all data is fully annotated.",
    "Due to annotation cost and the practical requirement that subsequent tasks like distance measurement and risk assessment rely on overall object contours, the hollows between steel wires inside the objects have not been accurately annotated.",
    "During evaluation, we follow the promptable segmentation paradigm as in HQSeg-44K, where each object is individually segmented based on the given bounding box prompt.",
    "As modern detectors can provide high-accuracy boxes in real-time, we focus on category-agnostic promptable segmentation."
  ]
}